STARTRC Universal Drone Storage Shoulder bag for DJI Mini 3 pro with RC-N1 Remote Controller Outdoor Backpack drone Accessories
1. This travel shoulder bag is designed a variety of DJI unmanned drone and their accessories, like DJI Mini 3 pro/ DJI Mavic 3/ DJI Air 2S/ DJI Mini 2/DJI Mavic Air 2, making them well-organized, compact and comfortable to carry;
2. The internal partition design can easily accommodate the aircraft + remote control + two batteries + butler + charger + blade + data cable, a package of multi-energy;
3. Optimized design for outdoor scenes such as diagonal straddle, to reduce the burden of travel and facilitate access to items;
4. The outer bag can be used to store the mobile phone charging bank, etc., which is more convenient to travel.

Please notice this is only the bag, not include drone or other accessories.

